com.communote.server.core.security

Class FieldUserIdentification

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.communote.server.core.security.FieldUserIdentification
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UserIdentification

    public class FieldUserIdentification
extends Object
implements UserIdentification
    A UserIdentification that is map holding some attributes. For now only the alias is supported by the core. However other plugins may store additional attributes that ExternalUserRepos may interpret.
    Author:
    Communote GmbH - http://www.communote.com/
